{"tid":832031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老竇喺大中華膠，可以點勸佢唔好再支持共產黨？","createTime":"2018-09-22T13:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T14:09:42.000Z","uid":5735,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e023e120316aefa34e3e69ea82203c192fbbe78","tid":832031,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"我老豆係一個藍絲大中華膠，成撚日就係到批評年輕人啲思想，話我地俾人洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時廢事同佢嘈，所以從來都唔同佢講政治。因為以前講過幾次，唔夠講就話我唔係經濟學家，唔係律師點樣評論中國經濟同埋法律問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後就發脾氣<br />\n但係呢排就開始係到講然後問我意見，我完全唔知點答佢，唔想係飯枱鬧交。但係聽佢講真係人都燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野反對一地兩檢係戇鳩，香港係中國一部分，一地一檢都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話應該割咗先，唔得先再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩用成千億起架濕鳩動車好正常可以融合國家，淨係快幾分鐘唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話成千億無問題，無證據話咩貪污受賄送錢之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係度問我話信唔信有外國勢力支持民主派，我心諗你不如問下建制派有冇收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要話我，叫我唔好成日睇d咁偏激嘅嘢，唔好睇毒果，睇野中立啲，但係佢自己就睇HKG報，巴士的報同埋睇CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽咗成程真係好撚嬲，但係廢事係阿嬤面前同老豆開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打有咩意見可以點樣令我老竇正常啲，定係我應該放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23d8ae76a6facf910bbb731190f29eff1cf1c8e","tid":832031,"uid":198622,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2ef318054138c1fb0a68e30ed6b00677d653761","tid":832031,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b23d8ae76a6facf910bbb731190f29eff1cf1c8e","tid":832031,"uid":198622,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ac4358fcb97c739d6aff351ddb20789426b416","tid":832031,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打幫拖<br />\n認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abff19091e2f5da46e61490a34d1c344b308230c","tid":832031,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"改變唔到架啦，求其hea應附和幾句咪得囉，咁認真做乜。再追問咪話自己政治冷感無留意囉"},{"pid":"71e5e94bffd2f8b973103a5e25dae6bc22041394","tid":832031,"uid":128514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"問下佢點睇六四, 還有近日既毒疫苗, 如果佢仍然覺得係中共有問題證明佢仲有得救!"},{"pid":"76b5b910cae07594bfb83492a9092b8795cd28b6","tid":832031,"uid":29041,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"爹親娘親不如毛主席親<br />\n熟讀毛語錄，再批鬥你老豆"},{"pid":"b6dccda59dc9154214273f734b3dd1c01cc9e0a4","tid":832031,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"你話你手上大把美股，美國佬唔千秋萬代你個仔就要乞食，連家用都比唔起"},{"pid":"e849885d23f94122dd0538265b9e71366d88d92a","tid":832031,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71e5e94bffd2f8b973103a5e25dae6bc22041394","tid":832031,"uid":128514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"問下佢點睇六四, 還有近日既毒疫苗, 如果佢仍然覺得係中共有問題證明佢仲有得救!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"我記得佢有講過中共唔好<br />\n但係話咩13億人嘅社會史無前例<br />\n要摸住石頭過河<br />\n共產黨已經好好㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfa73df5d2a66db98fe154b759c4ed413359ac